oads/2024/02/Godspeed-You-Black-Emperor-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Godspeed-You-Black-Emperor-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Godspeed-You-Black-Emperor-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Godspeed-You-Black-Emperor-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Godspeed-You-Black-Emperor-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Godspeed-You-Black-Emperor-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/godspeed-you-black-emperor">祝你好运！ BlackEmperor</a>在拉开 2024 年世界巡演序幕的同时推出了三首全新曲目。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/godspeed-you-black-emperor-g_ds-pee-at-states-end-review-2911089">祝你好运！黑皇帝 – “G_d&#39;s Pee AT STATE&#39;s END”评论：动荡时代的音乐</a></strong></li></ul><p>该乐队于 2 月 26 日星期六在纽约皇后区的 Knockdown 中心拉开了 2024 年大型巡演的序幕。在登上舞台时，他们为演出参加者带来了三首尚未发行的新曲目。据<a href="https://www.brooklynvegan.com/godspeed-you-black-emperor-debuted-3-new-songs-at-tour-kickoff-at-knockdown-center-listen-pics-2024-dates/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Brooklyn Vegan》</em></a>报道，乐队的大部分曲目都专注于冗长的全新曲目。</p><p>粉丝们很快就根据乐队表演每首曲目时在后面播放的投影给新曲目起了“花朵”、“火焰”和“羽毛”的绰号。看看下面的内容。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="祝你好运！黑皇帝 - 新歌#1“花” (2024-02-24)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CnMxEOxS_bE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="祝你好运！黑皇帝 - 新歌#2“Flames” (2024-02-24)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TZ7kM_MzqGQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>